These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, reading
House: palace, cape-cod
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, malaysian
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, train
2 different games are played: poker, canasta
1. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the cape-cod house is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| Flower          | lily  | zinnia     |
| Hobby         | reading    | chess         |
| House           | palace    | cape-cod |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | malaysian     |
| Transport           | train      | roller    |
| Game         | canasta | poker          |

