.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, writing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, december
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, western
House: victorian, wooden
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, game
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, van
1. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby         | dancing      | writing       |
| Birthday           | june | december |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | horror        |
| House   | victorian         | wooden        |
| Cigar   | dunhill    | game       |
| Beverage           | sprite        | almond-milk          |
| Transport     | van          | snowmobile    |

