The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret
House: tower, townhouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, family
1. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the tower house##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | soy-milk  |
| Flower          | amaryllis   | dahlia   |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles   |
| Pet           | rabbit        | ferret   |
| House   | townhouse      | tower |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | climbing  |
| Movie-Genre     | western       | family      |

