3. the person traveling to boston is the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating peas##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |
| City      | rome      | boston |
